		{
			dependencies: ["7A03000000000102"]
			description: [
				"&8[ RESEARCH LOG — THE LIVING WORKSHOP ]&r"
				""
				"&7They did not tend their magic by hand. They bound small spirits to the work — gathering, growing, generating Source while no one watched.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: build a Ritual Brazier, bind a Drygmy, and set up a Sourcelink to generate Source on its own.&r"
			]
