			description: [
				"&8[ RECOVERED DOCUMENT — SPOKEN MAGIC ]&r"
				""
				"&7A different school entirely. They wrote power into scrolls and books and carried it like a weapon. The inscription tools survive; the restraint that was meant to accompany them does not.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: build an Inscription Table and a Scroll Forge. Bind a spell to a scroll.&r"
			]
			icon: "irons_spellbooks:inscription_table"
