			dependencies: ["7A03000000000103"]
			description: [
				"&8[ RECOVERED DOCUMENT — BORROWED HANDS ]&r"
				""
				"&7Once the first spirit answered, the rest was industry. They put the summoned to work: mining, hauling, keeping a storehouse that held far more than its walls should allow.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: raise a Storage Controller, a Dimensional Storage Actuator's lamp, and a Satchel to carry the network with you.&r"
