			description: [
				"&8[ RECOVERED DOCUMENT — THE BOUND SERVANT ]&r"
				""
				"&7The deeper texts describe binding a spirit to a person, not a task. A familiar. A companion that was, the notes insist, never truly owned.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: craft a Familiar Ring, a Dimensional Matrix, and a Stable Wormhole. Ask, and see what answers.&r"
