			description: [
				"&8[ FIELD NOTE — THE BROOM AND THE CAULDRON ]&r"
				""
				"&7The folk practice had its own tools, humble and effective. A cauldron for brewing, jars of dried herbs, and — the notes are quite serious about this — a broom that flies.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: craft a Willow Broom, a Herb Jar, and a Candle Dipper. Work the old way.&r"
